  "performance": {
    "notes": "Micro-timing creates human feel. Kick timing varies slightly (-5 to +3 ticks). Snare is Push (ahead by +10 ticks offset). Hi-hats are Pull (behind by -5 ticks offset, individual notes -5 to -10). Creates natural, organic groove.",
